      <title>惠誉预计印度卢比兑美元汇率将因债券流入而反弹至 82 卢比</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-08/fitch-sees-india-rupee-rebounding-to-82-per-dollar-on-bond-inflows</link>
      <description><![CDATA[惠誉评级表示，潜在的大量外资流入印度债券将有助于卢比从接近历史低点反弹，但该国央行可能会限制其涨幅。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-08/fitch-sees-india-rupee-rebounding-to-82-per-dollar-on-bond-inflows</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 08 May 2024 01:30:00 GMT</pubDate>
