      <pubDate>Wed, 08 May 2024 00:46:42 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>先生。财政部长姆努钦谈拜登的政策、赤字和美元</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-05-08/fmr-treasury-secretary-mnuchin-on-biden-s-policies-deficits-dollar</link>
      <description><![CDATA[前财政部长史蒂文·姆努钦分享了他对拜登政府的经济政策、财政赤字和美元的看法。他还谈到了美国扣押的俄罗斯主权资产。他接受了彭博电视台的大卫·威斯汀的采访。 （来源：彭博社）]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-05-08/fmr-treasury-secretary-mnuchin-on-biden-s-policies-deficits-dollar</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 08 May 2024 00:32:43 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>Olam Agri 击败路易达孚收购棉花生产商 Namoi</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-07/olam-agri-trumps-louis-dreyfus-bid-for-cotton-producer-namoi</link>
      <description><![CDATA[奥兰农业控股有限公司（Olam Agri Holdings Ltd.）再次击败了路易达孚公司（Louis Dreyfus Co.）对纳莫伊棉花有限公司（Namoi Cotton Ltd.）的收购，两大农业贸易商争夺这家澳大利亚棉花生产商。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-07/olam-agri-trumps-louis-dreyfus-bid-for-cotton-producer-namoi</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 07 May 2024 23:45:53 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>由于美国库存和中东紧张局势成为焦点，石油价格下跌</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-07/latest-oil-market-news-and-analysis-for-may-8</link>
      <description><![CDATA[受美国库存报告略微利空且中东紧张局势成为焦点，油价跌至3月中旬以来的最低水平附近。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-07/latest-oil-market-news-and-analysis-for-may-8</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 07 May 2024 23:29:01 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>亚洲股市小幅走低，盈利成为焦点：市场总结</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-07/stock-market-today-dow-s-p-live-updates</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在美国股市低迷之后，亚洲股市下跌，投资者在进一步推动本月的上涨之前寻求盈利复苏的确凿证据。]]></description>
